  "text": "PUs show a wide range of shapes and many differences in the type or density of internal contacts. These characteristics are related to internal energy. To evaluate stability and contact energy, we implemented the DOPE statistical potential [CITATION_1] to compute the pseudo-energy of PUs. This value gives an approximation of the internal energy of PUs and insight on the structural significance of observed PUs.",
